Package: smartdiskdoctor
Version: 2.0.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, 
         python3-pyqt6, 
         smartmontools, 
         coreutils, 
         util-linux
Maintainer: A. Serhat KILICOGLU <https://github.com/shampuan>
Description: Smart Disk Doctor (formerly Zeus HDD Doctor)
 A utility for monitoring storage health using SMART data.
 This program checks the health of mechanical disks and SSDs, 
 providing detailed SMART information and secure erase features.
